    (comment 1 "Pinout real probado TCRT D3/D2/D0")
    (comment 2 "No PCB personalizada; montaje sobre Shield")
  )
  (text "ARDUINO NANO + EXPANSION I/O SHIELD\nD0 usado por TCRT Back; D1 libre para TX Serial.\nTodos los modulos comparten GND comun."
    (at 20 25 0)
    (effects (font (size 2 2) (bold yes)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111")
  )
  (rectangle (start 18 30) (end 190 55)
    (stroke (width 0.25) (type solid)) (fill (type none))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111112")
  )
  (text "POWER\nVCC_5V -> HC-SR04, TCRT5000, KY-012\nVCC_SERVO -> SG90 Left/Right, verificar corriente\nGND -> comun para Arduino, sensores, buzzer y servos"
    (at 22 42 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111113")
  )
  (rectangle (start 18 62) (end 95 94)
    (stroke (width 0.25) (type solid)) (fill (type none))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111114")
  )
  (text "HC-SR04\nVCC -> VCC_5V\nGND -> GND\nTrig -> D4 / TRIG_HCSR04\nEcho -> D5 / ECHO_HCSR04"
    (at 22 75 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111115")
  )
  (rectangle (start 105 62) (end 190 108)
    (stroke (width 0.25) (type solid)) (fill (type none))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111116")
  )
  (text "TCRT5000\nLeft DO -> D3 / TCRT_LEFT\nRight DO -> D2 / TCRT_RIGHT\nBack DO -> D0 / TCRT_BACK\nCada modulo: VCC_5V y GND"
    (at 110 78 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111117")
  )
  (rectangle (start 18 112) (end 95 145)
    (stroke (width 0.25) (type solid)) (fill (type none))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111118")
  )
  (text "SG90 SERVOS\nLeft signal -> D9 / SERVO_LEFT\nRight signal -> D10 / SERVO_RIGHT\nSolo traccion si son rotacion continua."
    (at 22 126 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111119")
  )
  (rectangle (start 105 116) (end 190 145)
    (stroke (width 0.25) (type solid)) (fill (type none))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111120")
  )
  (text "KY-012 BUZZER\nSignal -> D7 / BUZZER_SIG\nVCC -> VCC_5V\nGND -> GND"
    (at 110 128 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111121")
  )
  (text "NOTAS\n1. D0 comparte RX Serial; desconectar TCRT Back si interfiere con carga.\n2. Verificar corriente de servos SG90.\n3. La Shield facilita conexion, pero no aumenta capacidad de corriente."
    (at 20 164 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.45 1.45)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111122")
  )
